        "content": "<p>Oh no, nevermind... I just got the arguments in the wrong order!</p>\n<p>The following is fine:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">algebra.algebra.basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">E</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm_group</span> <span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">fooâ‚</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">has_add</span> <span class=\"n\">E</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">apply_instance</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- works</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">semiring</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">fooâ‚ƒ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">has_scalar</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">E</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">apply_instance</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- works</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
